 Nori Productions的负责人佃纪夫将针对VTuber的毕业和个人化问题发表说明。 https://p2y.jp/noripro-leader-tsukudani-norio-held-an-explanatory-streaming-following-the-graduation-and-independence-of-affiliated-vtuber/ https://p2y.jp/noripro-leader-tsukudani-norio-held-an-explanatory-streaming-following-the-graduation-and-independence-of-affiliated-vtuber/#respondp2y_admin Tue, 21 Nov 2023 20:50:12 +0000 VTuberバーチャルYouTubeYouTuberのりプロバーチャルYouTuber佃煮のりお姫咲ゆずる愛宮みるく犬山たまき猫瀬乃しん白雪みしろ https://p2y.jp/?p=106933 <p>经营VTuber经纪公司NoriPro的佃纪男（VTuber犬山环的表演者/声优）于2023年11月22日宣布，同属经纪公司的白雪美白郎和爱宫弥留也将加入她的队伍。 ……]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/noripro-leader-tsukudani-norio-held-an-explanatory-streaming-following-the-graduation-and-independence-of-affiliated-vtuber/">Nori Pro 社长佃纪男 (Norio Tsukudani) 的帖子，在 VTuber 毕业并成为个人后发布了一份说明。首次</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> VTuber办公室<strong>NoriPro</strong>负责人<strong>佃纪男</strong>（VTuber犬山环的表演者/声优模特）于2023年11月22日宣布，她将加入同一经纪公司的<strong>白雪美白郎、</strong><strong>爱宫弥留</strong>、<strong>姫咲结弦</strong>、以及<strong>Shin Nekoseno</strong>的毕业和个人才能（独立）的转变，发表了解释。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1100" height="619" data-attachment-id="100132" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-noripro-makes-major-announcements-including-1st-audition/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="VTuber办公室Nori Pro发布重要公告，包括首次举行试镜" class="wp-image-100132" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">佃纪男 图片来源： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lw6OCs_rkPY" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="YouTube">YouTube</a><br> © 诺里临</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>Nori Pro于11月20日宣布，旗下艺人白雪三白郎、爱宫弥留、姫咲结弦、猫濑野真将于12月底毕业，并于2024年1月（令和6）起成为个人艺人。执行为</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="w9uQ6oU7kj"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/">Nori Pro 的 VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nori Pro VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/embed/#?secret=eFCLlIqqfX#?secret=w9uQ6oU7kj" data-secret="w9uQ6oU7kj" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此外，当天，白雪三代郎、爱宫弥留、姫咲结弦、猫濑野真根据Nori Pro的官方公告进行了分发。虽然他明确表示并不是因为对经纪公司不满而辞职，但由于合同原因，他无法透露原因，所以一些观众和粉丝可能会想，“<em>其实他是在良好的条件下毕业的。”</em> 「<em>难道不是这样吗？」</em>以及「<em>我没有听到任何人才对佃谷纪夫表示感谢。」</em>看来确实如此。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="AOHzzLXXvq"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/streaming-by-4-vtubers-shirayuki-mishiro-enomiya-milk-himesaki-yuzuru-and-nekozeno-shin-who-will-graduate-from-noripro/">Nori Pro 毕业 VTubers Mishiro Shirayuki、Miruku Aimiya、Yuzuru Himesaki 和 Shin Nekoseno 即将播出</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nori Pro 毕业 VTubers Mishiro Shirayuki、Miruku Aimiya、Yuzuru Himesaki 和 Shin Nekoseno 将进行直播” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/streaming-by-4-vtubers-shirayuki-mishiro-enomiya-milk-himesaki-yuzuru-and-nekozeno-shin-who-will-graduate-from-noripro/embed/#?secret=NzVglHzdOa#?secret=AOHzzLXXvq" data-secret="AOHzzLXXvq" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="mzhcq655d29bfae6fe" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
